  <brief_title>Laryngeal Mask or Endotracheal Tube for Back Surgery in the Prone Position</brief_title>
  <official_title>Laryngeal Mask or Endotracheal Tube for Back Surgery in the Prone Position. Advantages, Adverse Effects and Time Consumation for the Two Methods.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
